<man name="waitForTurn" long-name="Break the current script until the actor finished turning">
	<description>	
	
	
	Break the current script until the actor finished turning. WARNING: ScummVM
	have a dirty hack bcs of some problems in the dig. See scumm/script\_v6.cpp
	for more details. If the actor have an id such that actor % 45 == 0 the hack
	will kick in and the current actor will be used instead.
	
	
	</description>
	<command name="waitForTurn">
		<file name="actor" required="true"/>
	</command>
	<see-also>
<cmd>waitForActor</cmd>, <cmd>waitForMessage</cmd>, <cmd>waitForCamera</cmd>, <cmd>waitForSentence</cmd>, <cmd>waitForAnimation</cmd>	</see-also>
</man>